==Example Text==
The string "HERO" would be encoded as:
<pre>
$87 $84 $91 $8e $00
 H   E   R   O  END
</pre>

The string "Hello!" would be:
<pre>
$87 $9e $a5 $a5 $a8 $be $00
 H   e   l   l   o   !  END
</pre>

==Compression==
Dialogue text may use a form of dictionary compression where common words/phrases are replaced with single-byte tokens that expand to full strings.

